sub_title: Open to work as UX Designer.
summary:
I aspire to be an effective UI/UX or Visual Design team member. I have a passion for UX design, mobile app design, responsive website design, and user research. I feel a true devotion toward typography and color.

To this end, I have spent 6 months working as an ideal UX designer by developing three projects for getting Google UX Design Certificate. This includes two mobile apps and two responsive website designs.

I love UX design and the people working in this field. I identify with the people who have the same passion for what we do
            
- I build user-centered and engaging content for web and mobile

- I like to understand the audiences and build experiences

- I think of accessibility as an essential part of the creative experience

Before this, I had 3 years of experience working as a freelance voice actor in Bangladeshi media.
